data.description: Do not miss this beautiful 4 bedroom home priced to sell in desirable Bradshaw Crossing subdivision. This home boasts an open floor plan with a spacious master bedroom on main with ensuite including dual vanity, sperate bath/shower and large walk-in close.  Three additional bedroom are on second floor.    Second story also has a nice living room, game room or office space.  The lovely kitchen has granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Nice covered back patio and good-sized backyard.   There is NO carpet in this home as it boasts wood, laminate and tile flooring.  Great location with community pool & park! This home is awesome for commuting both into and out of Austin.  Added bonus...this location  has great proximity to many outdoor activities, such as, Onion Creek Metropolitan Park, Mckinney Falls State Park, and Mary Moore Searight Metropolitan Park.  Southpark Meadow is a mere 3.5 miles away and offers shopping, dining and entertainment choices.
